That should be a simple change, just add the value to the scenario file and
load it in when that scenario is played.
Maybe go a bit further and have some options for what should happen when the
limit is hit (ie never generate any more, generate more as they die, or wait
for a timer to expire before checking again) - that way you could create
things like attack waves.

- Deathifier

